§ INTEGRATION-MIGRATION (refactor-plan @ wave-7+ · per-crate)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ MIGRATION-LEVEL-1 (UNIFIED-DETERMINISM)
  refactor : every-crate-using-PCG-32-locally → consume cssl-substrate canonical-RNG-handle
  affected : cssl-host-procgen-rooms · cssl-host-fab-procgen · cssl-host-input-virtual
  pattern : `pub fn procgen_with_substrate_rng(rng_handle: SubstrateRngHandle, ...) -> Recipe`
  benefit : seed-coherence across-systems · same-Substrate-state → same-procgen-output everywhere

§ MIGRATION-LEVEL-2 (UNIFIED-CRYPTO)
  refactor : every-crate-using-FNV-1a-128-locally → upgrade to BLAKE3-from-substrate-canonical
  affected : cssl-host-golden · cssl-host-asset-bundle (currently FNV-1a-128 stub)
  preserve : the FNV-fp stays for fast-comparison · adds BLAKE3 as canonical-content-hash
  benefit : cross-substrate-attestation · interoperable-Merkle-proofs

§ MIGRATION-LEVEL-3 (ω-FIELD-CONSUMPTION)
  refactor : crates currently-passing-around-POD-data refactor to consume FieldCell-handles when available
  affected : cssl-host-causal-seed (story-as-physics is-naturally-ω-field-events) · cssl-host-procgen-rooms (room-recipes-as-Σ-mask-stamps) · cssl-host-cocreative (bias-vector-as-KAN-material)
  pattern : crates take optional `omega_field: Option<&OmegaFieldHandle>` · stage-0 falls-back to local-data
  benefit : runtime-procgen lives-in-substrate · ¬ duplicated-host-side state

§ MIGRATION-LEVEL-4 (HDC-SUMMARIZATION @ multi-system)
  introduce : every-crate emitting-events also emits 10000-D HDC-hypervector summary
  affected : cssl-host-attestation (per-session HDC-summary) · cssl-host-causal-seed (DAG-state HDC) · cssl-host-replay (replay HDC-fingerprint) · cssl-host-cocreative (bias HDC)
  benefit : O(1) cross-system similarity-check · fast-coherence-validation · enables Σ-Chain Coherence-Proof

§ MIGRATION-LEVEL-5 (WAVELET-MULTI-RES @ network-IO)
  introduce : every-crate-doing-network-egress (cssl-host-mp-transport · cssl-host-stripe-integration · cssl-host-multiverse-aggregate) sends MERA-coarse-summary first · drill-down on demand
  affected : Σ-Chain TIER-3 multiversal-stream · Bazaar-browse · Living-Multiverse-aesthetic-drift
  benefit : bandwidth-efficient sync · privacy-preserving (coarse-share-without-leaking-detail)

§ MIGRATION-LEVEL-6 (PGA-ROTOR @ state-transitions)
  introduce : state-transitions-that-rotate-naturally use PGA-rotors instead of-ad-hoc-quaternions
  affected : cssl-host-stereoscopy (eye-rotation) · cssl-host-anim-procedural (already substrate-side) · DM-orchestrator scene-rotations
  benefit : geometrically-meaningful · interoperable-with-physics-layer · uniform-API

